              </a>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/vojta_de_coninck/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-social-card bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 text-white p-4">
